<emphasis id="C0B3EA86FFCFFFFF2D258BE4FB5CFD34" box="[1134,1222,650,676]" italics="true" pageId="17">πεταλΟΝ</emphasis>
“petal”, in reference to the slender petals.
</paragraph>
